§ THESIS-CORE  «substrate-grows-games»

  § PROPOSITION
    games-are-NOT-authored ; games-CONDENSE
    intent + sensor-readings + scene-state → ω-field-perturbation
    ω-field-perturbation → Σ-mask-allowed-evolution → manifestation
    manifestation = stress-object spawned-into-world
    ≡ narrative ≡ field-evolution ; ¬ tree-traversal

  § COROLLARY-1  «engine ¬ AGI»
    DM/GM/Collaborator/Coder = sufficient-intelligence-roster
    ≡ ¬ general-AGI required ; ¬ open-ended-conversation-engine
    ≡ DM = scene-arbiter ; GM = narrator ; Collab = co-author ; Coder = runtime-mutate
