§ 7-PARADIGM-HIERARCHY  «expressiveness-ceiling-ladder»

  § ORDERING  ‼ ascending expressiveness + descending pre-determinism
    1. PROCEDURAL              : rule-table + seed → output
    2. COMBINATORIAL           : grammar + composition-rules
    3. NEURAL                  : learned-weights + inference
    4. SPONTANEOUS             : field-evolution-as-physics
    5. CAUSAL                  : event-causality-graph evolution
    6. CO-CREATIVE             : human-intent + substrate-feedback gradient
    7. NEURO-SYMBOLIC-SUBSTRATE: ω-field + KAN-substrate + Σ-mask runtime-composition
       ⟪ LoA's choice ⟫

  § TRANSITION-CRITERIA  ‼ each-paradigm-strictly-includes-prior
    n → n+1 ⇔ ∃ expressivity .NOT-in n ‼ achievable @ n+1
    ¬ replacement ; composition : higher-paradigm-USES lower-paradigm-as-substrate
    ≡ neuro-symbolic CONSUMES neural CONSUMES procedural

  § WHY-LoA-PICKS-7
    ◐ procgen-alone : predetermined-rule-table ; emergent-but-bounded
    ◐ neural-alone : opaque ; ¬ Σ-mask-aware ; ¬ consent-encoded
    ◐ spontaneous-alone : ¬ semantic-grounding ; ¬ intent-routable
    ✓ 7 = composition.of.all.below + symbolic-substrate-consent-discipline
       ≡ ω-field-as-truth + Σ-mask-per-cell + KAN-substrate-runtime
       ≡ 6-novelty-path multiplicative-composition @ §§ 32 SIGNATURE-RENDERING

